\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Comparison of simulated critical population sizes against the derived expected change in H for Moran process. Small deviations due to stochasticity in the simulations. $\gamma = 0.2, \beta = 0.1$ standard RPS. Small deviations due to random nature of simulations, but close match to analytical result. Drift reversal is present in the agent based simulations and exactly matching analytical prediction for these paremeters.}}{5}{}\protected@file@percent }
